I'm a composer, orchestrator, session bassist and music producer, I'm also an engineer (acoustic training) and a sound technician.

I have advanced studies in music composition, orchestration, music production and audio processing. I graduated from the National University of La Plata (UNLP), Argentina.

I offer my services as a composer, producer, arranger, transcriptionist, and session musician.
My services vary in a wide range of genres, such as Rock / Metal, Jazz, Pop, R&B, orchestral music, incidental music (film music), etc.
